@@$TJvCheckListBox
<GROUP JVCL.Miscel>
<TITLE TJvCheckListBox overview>
  TJvCheckListBox is an enhance TCheckListBox control that adds various features:

  * <LINK TJvCheckBox.HotTrack, Hot track> support.
  * A <LINK TJvCheckListBox.HorScrollbar, horizontal scroll bar>.
  * Events for both the <LINK TJvCheckListBox.OnHorizontalScroll, horizontal> as well as the
    <LINK TJvCheckListBox.OnHorizontalScroll, vertical> scrollbar.
  * Mechanism to search items based on <LINK TJvCheckListBox.SearchExactString, exact string>,
    <LINK TJvCheckListBox.SearchPrefix, start with a string> or
    <LINK TJvCheckListBox.SearchSubString, containing a string>.
  * Manipulating selections (<LINK TJvCheckListBox.SelectAll, all>,
    <LINK TJvCheckListBox.UnselectAll, none> or <LINK TJvCheckListBox.InvertSelection, invert>).
  * Manipulating check marks (<LINK TJvCheckListBox.CheckAll, all>,
    <LINK TJvCheckListBox.UnCheckall, none> or <LINK TJvCheckListBox.InvertCheck, invert>).
  * Conditional deletion (<LINK TJvCheckListBox.DeleteExactString, string matching>,
    <LINK TJvCheckListBox.DeleteSelected, selected>).
