@@TJvCheckListBox
<GROUP TJvCheckListBox>
Summary
  Enhanced TCheckListBox with hot track, horizontal scrollbar, searching, selection manipulation and
  checkmark mainulation.
Description
  TJvCheckListBox is an enhance TCheckListBox control that adds hot tracking effects, a horizontal
  scrollbar, searching, selection manipulation and manipulation on multiple check marks.

  For more information on how to use this component, check out the
  <LINK $TJvCheckListBox, overview>.
