@@TJvCheckListBox.GetChecked
Summary
  Retrieves a list of checked items.
Description
  GetChecked generates a string list with all items that are checked. If you have objects associated
  with the items (using the Objects property), these objects will also be present in the list.
Note
  GetChecked will create a new string list instance. The caller will be responsible of freeing the
  list when it's done with it.
See Also
  GetUnChecked
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCheckListBox.GetUnChecked
  Retrieves a list of unchecked items.
Description
  GetUnChecked generates a string list with all items that are not checked. If you have objects
  associated with the items (using the Objects property), these objects will also be present in the
  list.
Note
  GetUnChecked will create a new string list instance. The caller will be responsible of freeing the
  list when it's done with it.
See Also
  GetChecked
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
