@@TJvCheckListBox.SearchExactString
Summary
  Searches for an item using an exact string match.
Description
  SearchExactString searches for an item who's string matches that of the given string. You can
  specify if the matching should be done case sensitive or not.

  If an item is found, it's index will be returned, otherwise -1 will be returned.
Parameters
  Value -         The string to search for.
  CaseSensitive - Flag to signal if the matching should be case sensitive or not. If set to True,
                  matching is case sensitive, otherwise it's not.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCheckListBox.SearchPrefix
Summary
  Searches for an item that starts with the given string.
Description
  SearchPrefix will search for an item who's string starts with the given string. You can specify if
  the matching should be done case sensitive or not.

  If an item is found, it's index will be returned, otherwise -1 will be returned.
Parameters
  Value -         The string to search for.
  CaseSensitive - Flag to signal if the matching should be case sensitive or not. If set to True,
                  matching is case sensitive, otherwise it's not.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCheckListBox.SearchSubString
Summary
  Searches for an item that contains the given string.
Description
  SearchPrefix will search for an item who's string contains the given string. You can specify if
  the matching should be done case sensitive or not.

  If an item is found, it's index will be returned, otherwise -1 will be returned.
Parameters
  Value -         The string to search for.
  CaseSensitive - Flag to signal if the matching should be case sensitive or not. If set to True,
                  matching is case sensitive, otherwise it's not.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
