@@TJvCheckListBox.HorScrollbar
Summary
  Determines if a horizontal scrollbar is needed.
Description
  HorScrollbar indicates if a horizontal scrollbar should be shown when one or more items do not
  fit in the control.

  Set this property to True if you want a horizontal scrollbar.

  Set this property to False if you don't want a horizontal scrollbar, even if one or more items
  don't fit.
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
@@TJvCheckListBox.HotTrack
Summary
  Enables or disables hot tracking.
Description
  HotTrack determines if hot tracking is enabled or disabled. When hot tracking is enabled, the
  control will be flat, except when the mouse is over the control.

  Set HotTrack to True to enable hot tracking support.
